            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EIsaiah%201%3A1-2%3A22%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_1_1%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EIsaiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThese%20are%20the%20visions%20that%20Isaiah%20son%20of%20Amoz%20saw%20concerning%20Judah%20and%20Jerusalem.%20He%20saw%20these%20visions%20during%20the%20years%20when%20Uzziah%2C%20Jotham%2C%20Ahaz%2C%20and%20Hezekiah%20were%20kings%20of%20Judah.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20These%20kings%20reigned%20from%20792%20to%20686%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_1_2%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EA%20Message%20for%20Rebellious%20Judah%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EListen%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3Bheavens!%20Pay%20attention%2C%20earth!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20children%20I%20raised%20and%20cared%20for%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehave%20rebelled%20against%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_1_3%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EEven%20an%20ox%20knows%20its%20owner%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20a%20donkey%20recognizes%20its%20master%26%23x2019%3Bs%20care%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Ebut%20Israel%20doesn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20know%20its%20master.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EMy%20people%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20recognize%20my%20care%20for%20them.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_1_4%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EOh%2C%20what%20a%20sinful%20nation%20they%20are%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eloaded%20down%20with%20a%20burden%20of%20guilt.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20are%20evil%20people%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ecorrupt%20children%20who%20have%20rejected%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20have%20despised%20the%20Holy%20One%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20turned%20their%20backs%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_1_5%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EWhy%20do%20you%20continue%20to%20invite%20punishment%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EMust%20you%20rebel%20forever%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EYour%20head%20is%20injured%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20your%20heart%20is%20sick.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_1_6%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20are%20battered%20from%20head%20to%20foot%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ecovered%20with%20bruises%2C%20welts%2C%20and%20infected%20wounds%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewithout%20any%20soothing%20ointments%20or%20bandages.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_1_7%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EYour%20country%20lies%20in%20ruins%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20your%20towns%20are%20burned.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EForeigners%20plunder%20your%20fields%20before%20your%20eyes%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20destroy%20everything%20they%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_1_8%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EBeautiful%20Jerusalem%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A8%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EThe%20daughter%20of%20Zion.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20stands%20abandoned%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Elike%20a%20watchman%26%23x2019%3Bs%20shelter%20in%20a%20vineyard%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Elike%20a%20lean-to%20in%20a%20cucumber%20field%20after%20the%20harvest%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Elike%20a%20helpless%20city%20under%20siege.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22isai_1_9%22%20bk%3D%22isai%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehad%20not%20spared%20a%20few%20of%20us%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Greek%20version%20reads%20%3Cem%3Ea%20few%20of%20our%20children.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Compare%20Rom%209%3A29.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Ewe%20would%20have%20been%20wiped%20out%20like%20Sodom%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Edestroyed%20like%20Gomorrah.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20